<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <%- include('layout/head') %>
</head>
<body class="pb-24 pt-16 md:pt-20 animate-fade flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <%- include('layout/navbar') %>

    <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4 text-center">
        <div class="relative mb-8 animate-slide">
            <h1 class="text-[150px] font-black text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-500/20 to-transparent leading-none select-none">
                404
            </h1>
            <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 bg-zinc-800/80 backdrop-blur rounded-3xl border border-white/5 shadow-2xl flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-purple-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4m0 4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 max-w-md mx-auto animate-slide" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white">Halaman Tidak Ditemukan</h2>
            <p class="text-zinc-400">
                Sepertinya kamu tersesat di dimensi lain. Halaman yang kamu cari tidak ditemukan atau sudah dipindahkan.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4 animate-slide" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
            <button onclick="history.back()" class="px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 text-white text-sm font-medium hover:bg-white/5 transition">
                Kembali
            </button>
            <a href="/" class="px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full bg-white text-black text-sm font-bold hover:bg-zinc-200 transition shadow-lg shadow-purple-500/20">
                Ke Beranda
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
